        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Doctor: expose tool result cap findings",
        "body": "## Summary\n- add default-disabled structured lint findings for `core/doctor/tool-result-cap`\n- map existing toolResultMaxChars advice into warning findings with stable path/target/fixHint metadata\n- keep legacy `openclaw doctor` note output as the authority for normal Doctor runs\n\n## Public contract\n- No public SDK, plugin manifest, config schema, or persisted data-model contract changes.\n- The structured check is opt-in via `defaultEnabled: false`; default `doctor --lint` skips it while `--all` and `--only core/doctor/tool-result-cap` include it.\n- No repair path is added.\n\n## Validation\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/flows/doctor-tool-result-cap-advice.test.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.test.ts --reporter=verbose` (56 tests)\n- `pnpm exec oxfmt --write src/flows/doctor-tool-result-cap-advice.ts src/flows/doctor-tool-result-cap-advice.test.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.test.ts`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `node scripts/run-oxlint.mjs src/flows/doctor-tool-result-cap-advice.ts src/flows/doctor-tool-result-cap-advice.test.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.ts src/flows/doctor-health-contributions.test.ts`\n- `pnpm tsgo:core`\n- `OPENCLAW_CHECK_CHANGED_REMOTE_CHILD=1 OPENCLAW_CHANGED_LANES_RAW_SYNC=1 CI=1 pnpm check:changed`\n- `node scripts/plugin-sdk-surface-report.mjs --check`\n- `node scripts/check-plugin-sdk-exports.mjs`\n\n## Real behavior proof\nSource CLI proof with isolated `OPENCLAW_CONFIG_PATH` containing `agents.defaults.contextLimits.toolResultMaxChars = 16000`:\n\n- default `pnpm --silent openclaw doctor --lint --json`: `checksRun: 25`, `checksSkipped: 8`, `toolResultCapFindings: 0`\n- explicit `pnpm --silent openclaw doctor --lint --json --only core/doctor/tool-result-cap`: `checksRun: 1`, `checksSkipped: 32`, finding path `agents.defaults.contextLimits.toolResultMaxChars`, target `agents.defaults`, severity `warning`\n\n## Notes\n`pnpm check:changed` first tried to delegate to Blacksmith Testbox and was blocked by the local Crabbox binary version (`0.15.0`, requires `>=0.22.0`), so I ran the documented local child path directly with `OPENCLAW_CHECK_CHANGED_REMOTE_CHILD=1`.\n",
